oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Annie A. Moore correspondence with Mrs. Ames, 1862 November 21
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Moore, Annie A.; Sharples, H. R.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Letter dated 1862 November 21, from Annie A. Moore to Mrs. Ames thanking her for donations of money and clothing made by Mrs. Ames and her husband and also telling her about “Aunty Bigelow’s” illness. There is an addendum to the letter by H. R. Sharples also referencing the donations and Mrs. Bigelow’s illness.
